---
date: 
  created: {{ end_date.isoformat() }}
description: "{{ posts|length }} posts from {{ start_date }} to {{ end_date }}"
hide:
  - navigation
  - toc
---

# {% if logo_url %}<img src="{{ logo_url }}" alt="" style="height:1.2em;vertical-align:middle"> {% endif %}{{ feed_name }} Digest — {{ week_id }}

Posts from **{{ start_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}** to **{{ end_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}**. Total: **{{ posts|length }}** posts.

<!-- more -->

---

{% for post in posts %}
## **{{ loop.index }}. Post by `@{{ post.author_handle }}` on {{ post.date }}**

<div class="bsky-card" markdown="1">

<div class="bsky-header" markdown="1">
{% if post.author_avatar %}
<img src="{{ post.author_avatar }}" class="bsky-avatar">
{% endif %}
<div class="bsky-author-meta" markdown="1">
**{{ post.author_name }}** [@{{ post.author_handle }}]({{ post.author_url }}){:target="_blank"}
<br><small>{{ post.date }}</small>
</div>
</div>

<div class="bsky-content" markdown="1">

{{ post.text }}

{# --- Image Gallery Fix --- #}
{% if post.embed_images %}
<div class="bsky-image-grid bsky-grid-{{ post.embed_images|length }}" markdown="1">

{% for img in post.embed_images %}
{# The { .bsky-img } part requires the 'attr_list' extension in mkdocs.yml #}
![{{ img.alt | replace('\n', ' ') | e }}]({{ img.url }}){ .bsky-img }
{% endfor %}

</div>
{% endif %}

{# --- Link Preview (Card-in-Card) Fix --- #}
{% if post.embed_links %}
{% for link in post.embed_links %}
<a href="{{ link.uri }}" class="bsky-link-preview-wrapper" target="_blank">
<div class="bsky-link-preview" markdown="1">
{% if link.thumb %}
<img src="{{ link.thumb }}" class="link-thumb">
{% endif %}
<div class="link-info" markdown="1">
{% if link.title %}**{{ link.title }}**{% endif %}
{% if link.description %}<p class="link-desc">{{ link.description }}</p>{% endif %}
<small>:material-link: {{ link.uri | truncate(50) }}</small>
</div>
</div>
</a>
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

</div>

<div class="bsky-footer" markdown="1">
<div class="bsky-stats" markdown="1">
:material-heart: {{ post.likes }} &nbsp; :material-repeat: {{ post.reposts }} &nbsp; :material-comment: {{ post.replies }}
</div>
[View on Bluesky :material-open-in-new:]({{ post.bsky_url }}){ .md-button .md-button--primary }
</div>

</div>
{% endfor %}